"{\"uid\": \"horseandhound.co.uk-news-australian-olympic-eventer-shane-rose-begins-rehab-857301\", \"entities\": [{\"sentence\": \"Australian medal-winning riderShane Rosehas begun rehabilitation for his significant injuries, as he keeps his eyes on his sixthOlympic Games.\", \"from\": 0, \"to\": 142, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 0, \"end\": 10, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Australians\", \"score\": 0.9831455757655353, \"rank\": 0.014959257795887715, \"text\": \"Australian\", \"types\": [\"Q41710\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Australians\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Australians\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"On 14 March Shane was injured in a cross-country schooling accident, which resulted in surgery for a \\\"badly broken\\\" femur and fractured pelvis.\", \"from\": 144, \"to\": 287, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"He also suffered a \\\"heavy\\\" concussion and broken ribs in the fall.\", \"from\": 288, \"to\": 354, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"At the time a spokesman for Shane said \\\"while the timing is unfortunate we are hopeful there is adequate time for him to recover and still be able to continue his preparation schedule for Paris\\\".\", \"from\": 358, \"to\": 553, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 386, \"end\": 391, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Shane_McMahon\", \"score\": 0.9999850015737323, \"rank\": 1.4972087000018069e-05, \"text\": \"Shane\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Shane_McMahon\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Shane_McMahon\"}, {\"begin\": 546, \"end\": 551, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 0.9999969265626923, \"rank\": 3.073446806478296e-06, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"In an update today (3 May) Shane's team announced he has \\\"moved into the rehabilitation phase of his recovery\\\", and has become a resident at the Australian Institute of Sport in Canberra.\", \"from\": 555, \"to\": 742, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 733, \"end\": 741, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Canberra\", \"score\": 0.9999785850615093, \"rank\": 2.080528317672564e-05, \"text\": \"Canberra\", \"types\": [\"Q515\", \"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Canberra\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Canberra\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"His current daily life comprises intensive strength and conditioning sessions and medical treatments,\\\" said the spokesman, adding that Shane has been \\\"very fortunate to receive outstanding medical care since his accident\\\".\", \"from\": 746, \"to\": 969, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 882, \"end\": 887, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Shane_McMahon\", \"score\": 0.9999850015737323, \"rank\": 1.4972087000018069e-05, \"text\": \"Shane\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Shane_McMahon\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Shane_McMahon\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"He is very thankful to the New South Wales Institute of Sport, the Australian Institute of Sport and the Equestrian Australia high performance program, who have all been incredibly supportive and ensured he has access to the best doctors, physiotherapists and recovery treatments.\\\"\", \"from\": 971, \"to\": 1253, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1077, \"end\": 1097, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Equestrian_Australia\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Equestrian Australia\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Equestrian_Australia\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Equestrian_Australia\"}, {\"begin\": 1077, \"end\": 1097, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Equestrian_Australia\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Equestrian Australia\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Equestrian_Australia\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Equestrian_Australia\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The spokesman added that Shane's medical team have worked together and developed a program that will give him \\\"the best chance of recovering in time to pursue his Olympic ambitions\\\".\", \"from\": 1255, \"to\": 1437, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1280, \"end\": 1285, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Shane_McMahon\", \"score\": 0.9999850015737323, \"rank\": 1.4972087000018069e-05, \"text\": \"Shane\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Shane_McMahon\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Shane_McMahon\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The first day of the Olympic eventing competition is 27 July.\", \"from\": 1438, \"to\": 1499, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"Shane is motivated and working hard with the aim of being back in the saddle later this month,\\\" he said.\", \"from\": 1501, \"to\": 1606, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Shane is a three-time Olympic medallist and Paris 2024 would mark his sixth Games.\", \"from\": 1608, \"to\": 1690, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1652, \"end\": 1662, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2024_Summer_Olympics\", \"score\": 0.9999999999952252, \"rank\": 4.726132735538942e-12, \"text\": \"Paris 2024\", \"types\": [\"Q1656682\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2024_Summer_Olympics\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2024_Summer_Olympics\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"He won team silver with All Luck at Beijing in 2008, team bronze on CP Qualified at Rio 2016, and was part of the silver medal-winning team with Virgil inTokyo.\", \"from\": 1691, \"to\": 1851, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1727, \"end\": 1734, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2008_Summer_Olympics\", \"score\": 0.9999999691544876, \"rank\": 3.08455925710382e-08, \"text\": \"Beijing\", \"types\": [\"Q1656682\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2008_Summer_Olympics\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2008_Summer_Olympics\"}, {\"begin\": 1836, \"end\": 1842, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Virgil\", \"score\": 0.9325887731622186, \"rank\": 0.06678541557488073, \"text\": \"Virgil\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q36180\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Virgil\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Virgil\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"You might also be interested in:        Horse & Hound magazine, out every Thursday, is packed with all the latest news and reports, as well as interviews, specials, nostalgia, vet and training advice.\", \"from\": 1853, \"to\": 2053, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Find how you can enjoythe magazine deliveredto your door every week, plus options to upgrade your subscription to access ouronline servicethat brings you breaking news and reports as well as other benefits.\", \"from\": 2054, \"to\": 2260, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Stay in touch with all the news in the run-up to and throughout the major shows and events during 2025 and beyond with a Horse & Hound subscription.Subscribe todayfor all you need to know ahead of these major events, plus online reports on the action as it happens from our\\u00a0expert team of reporters\\u00a0and in-depth analysis in our special commemorative magazines.\", \"from\": 2262, \"to\": 2622, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2383, \"end\": 2396, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Horse_&_Hound\", \"score\": 0.9999999999877218, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Horse & Hound\", \"types\": [\"Q41298\", \"Q386724\", \"Q234460\", \"Q1092563\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Horse_&_Hound\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Horse_&_Hound\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Have a subscription already?Set up your\\u00a0unlimited website access now\", \"from\": 2623, \"to\": 2691, \"entities\": []}]}"